{
  "stem": "1400.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Nazis were hoping maybe because we are there, they will not be bombed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It would have been a short trip, but it took us almost three days to get to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What had happened, we got hit by air raid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They bombed the-- both of the tracks They machine-gunned our train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in the train where I was sitting, this time it wasn't so loaded.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were all squatting down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Both of the fellow beside me got hit by machine gunfire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I just dazed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "By then, the guards were gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We opened the railroad car and stumbled out of the car and walked into the woods nearby and hid there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember going out on the fields and dug up some potatoes for food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But they came back the next morning or a day later with dogs, gathered us together, and ordered us back to the railroad cars.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They never removed the bodies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This is how we arrived to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was past the-- or around 20th or 22nd of, of-- I know the date, because I know the liberation date.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Approximately on the 20th or 22nd of April, 1945, this is how we arrived to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they call this train the death train, because more dead bodies arrived to Dachau on this train than live ones.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was ordered into the camp, walked through the gate into the barracks, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and I don't know if I was there a week, five days or maybe 10 days, at the most.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Five days, a week.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we were liberated April 29 by the Seventh Army, as I learned later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "April 29, 1945.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was a glorious day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's hard to describe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were crying from happiness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I still intend to cry.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
